## English-version

# 🗃️ User Registration System — Version 1

> ⚠️ **This is version 1 of the project.**  
> It's still under development but already functional and presentable. Future improvements will be added.

## ✨ About the project

This is a complete **user registration system**, featuring a robust backend and full data validation.

While the frontend is still very simple (basic HTML with input fields), the backend is fully functional and secure. All field validators are implemented, with real-time error detection and **email verification before saving user data** to the database.

## 🚀 Features

- Full input validation
- Password confirmation
- Email verification link sending
- Data saved only after email confirmation
- Immediate error feedback on frontend

## 🛠️ Technologies used

- HTML5 (basic)
- CSS3 (minimal)
- Python
- Django
- SMTP (for email sending)

## 🧪 How to run the project

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/joaow0/user-registration.git

# Enter the folder
cd your-repo

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate the environment
# Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
# Linux/Mac:
source venv/bin/activate



# Set environment variables (.env)

# Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Start the server
python manage.py runserver
```

